WEBVTT

00:02.903 --> 00:03.902
[ Remote clicks ]

00:03.937 --> 00:05.504
[ Upbeat music plays ]

00:08.041 --> 00:10.943
♪ I don't care what you say! ♪

00:12.279 --> 00:14.246
♪ I'm gonna do what I want
all day! ♪

00:14.281 --> 00:16.848
♪ I'm the king of the world!
I'm the king of the world! ♪

00:16.883 --> 00:18.750
♪ I'm the king of the world!
I'm the king of the world! ♪

00:18.785 --> 00:21.020
♪ I'm the king of the world!
I'm the king of the world! ♪

00:29.429 --> 00:33.398
All right, Camden,
dare or die?

00:33.433 --> 00:35.934
Um...
D-die?

00:35.969 --> 00:37.169
He dies!

00:37.204 --> 00:38.203
Die!

00:38.238 --> 00:39.404
Ow, ow!

00:39.439 --> 00:41.273
[ Laughter ]

00:41.308 --> 00:42.874
How about you, Clarence?

00:42.909 --> 00:44.209
Dare or die?

00:44.244 --> 00:46.111
How's about...

00:46.146 --> 00:47.245
dare, please.

00:47.280 --> 00:49.047
He chose dare!

00:49.082 --> 00:50.715
Hmm.

00:50.750 --> 00:52.684
Make him eat the fuzzy bugs
again!

00:52.719 --> 00:54.619
Don't forget, Clarence has
a mild pollen allergy.

00:54.654 --> 00:57.089
Come on, give it back.

00:57.124 --> 00:58.924
Hey, no running!

00:58.959 --> 01:01.059
[ Grunts ]

01:01.094 --> 01:02.594
Ha ha!

01:02.629 --> 01:05.964
I dare you to steal one of
Miss Shoop's beans!

01:05.999 --> 01:07.399
That's scary!

01:07.434 --> 01:10.902
Oh, heh, easy!

01:10.937 --> 01:13.305
Yeah, he's dead.

01:13.340 --> 01:14.973
[ Growls ]
Hey, put that ball down!

01:15.008 --> 01:18.243
Okay, I just gotta
take one bean.

01:18.278 --> 01:20.712
Um, Ms. Shoop?

01:20.747 --> 01:22.280
No, no, no, no, no.

01:22.315 --> 01:25.550
Hey, Ms. Shoop.
- You look really handsome today.

01:25.585 --> 01:27.586
May I please have some beans?

01:27.621 --> 01:29.488
"Why, thank you, Clarence.

01:29.523 --> 01:30.889
You can have all the beans
you want."

01:30.924 --> 01:33.258
Thanks, Ms. Shoop.
Hmm?

01:33.293 --> 01:35.293
Shh.

01:35.328 --> 01:37.095
I'm hiding.

01:37.130 --> 01:38.930
[ Buzzes ]

01:38.965 --> 01:41.600
Just gotta wait for the right
moment.

01:41.635 --> 01:43.502
Get it -- get out of there!

01:43.537 --> 01:44.569
[ Gasps ]
Now!

01:44.604 --> 01:46.438
[ Screams ]

01:46.473 --> 01:48.640
You look really handsome today?

01:48.675 --> 01:50.108
Clarence, get away from me!

01:50.143 --> 01:51.176
[ Laughter ]

01:51.211 --> 01:52.944
She almost blew her lid.

01:52.979 --> 01:55.847
Yeah, you get a free pass
on that one.

01:55.882 --> 01:57.349
Ha ha!

01:57.384 --> 01:59.284
But I -- I still get that, yeah!

01:59.319 --> 02:04.022
Jeff, do you think Miss Shoop
has any friends?

02:04.057 --> 02:06.858
Well, of course not.
Miss Shoop is a terrible person.

02:06.893 --> 02:11.329
She's an awful, awful, awful,
awful, awful person.

02:11.364 --> 02:12.597
Yeah.
Shoop's no good.

02:12.632 --> 02:15.300
All right, Belson.
Dare or die?

02:15.335 --> 02:18.203
Um...
Meh.

02:18.238 --> 02:20.138
Hey, my game!

02:20.173 --> 02:21.273
Ow, ow!

02:21.308 --> 02:22.641
Stop it!
Oh!

02:24.010 --> 02:26.144
Clarence:
Aw, poor little thing.

02:26.179 --> 02:28.980
You're just a lonely little
Shoop, aren't you.

02:29.015 --> 02:31.950
[ Clicks tongue ]
So lonely in your lonely car...

02:31.985 --> 02:33.151
Clarence, what are you doing!

02:33.186 --> 02:34.553
Oh, uh...

02:34.588 --> 02:35.987
Uh, nothing.

02:36.022 --> 02:37.355
[ Tires squeal ]

02:37.390 --> 02:39.658
[ Grunting ]

02:39.693 --> 02:43.128
♪ Bring the beat back,
That's the beat I wanna hear ♪

02:43.163 --> 02:44.963
♪ When I get home
I take off my shoes ♪

02:44.998 --> 02:46.565
Whoa!

02:46.600 --> 02:49.534
[ Grunting to music ]

02:49.569 --> 02:51.736
[ Tires squeal ]

02:51.771 --> 02:54.172
♪ Feet on the floor
it's my slippers ♪

02:54.207 --> 02:56.708
[ Grunts ]

02:56.743 --> 02:59.311
Reporter: And in an ironic
twist, a fire truck

02:59.346 --> 03:02.080
caught on fire today in
downtown Aberdale.

03:02.115 --> 03:03.882
[ Laughs ]

03:03.917 --> 03:04.816
Huh?

03:04.851 --> 03:07.219
Oh, what?
Out of beans?

03:07.254 --> 03:09.321
Need more beans.

03:09.356 --> 03:11.723
Oh, poor Shoopy.

03:11.758 --> 03:14.326
You gotta get some seat buddies!

03:14.361 --> 03:15.927
Hmm.

03:15.962 --> 03:17.596
[ Doorbell rings ]
- Huh?

03:17.631 --> 03:20.265
What do you want?!
Uh, hi, Miss Shoop.

03:20.300 --> 03:24.836
Can I come to your party --
the one that you're having...

03:24.871 --> 03:25.870
now?

03:25.905 --> 03:28.340
What? What?!
No party! Go away!

03:28.375 --> 03:30.342
Wait, Miss Shoop, I can sit on
the couch with you!

03:30.377 --> 03:33.912
Hmm.

03:33.947 --> 03:36.881
[ Grunts ]
Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!

03:36.916 --> 03:38.450
Ow!

03:38.485 --> 03:40.252
Clarence, keep it down!

03:40.287 --> 03:42.020
Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!

03:42.055 --> 03:43.255
[ Growls ]

03:43.290 --> 03:45.423
You gotta get those prickers out
before you get infected!

03:45.458 --> 03:46.725
That's my advice.

03:46.760 --> 03:48.426
[ Lock clicks ]

03:48.461 --> 03:50.128
Hmm.

03:50.163 --> 03:51.696
[ Chuckles ]

03:51.731 --> 03:53.465
Feels all tingly.

03:53.500 --> 03:54.733
Ow!
- [ Sighs ]

03:54.768 --> 03:56.735
You can use the downstairs
bathroom.

03:56.770 --> 03:58.470
Five minutes.

03:58.505 --> 04:00.472
Whoa!

04:00.507 --> 04:02.407
What's this room for?

04:02.442 --> 04:03.408
Hmm? What?

04:03.443 --> 04:04.609
I don't use this room, come on.

04:04.644 --> 04:06.778
And take off your shoes!

04:09.115 --> 04:12.584
Whoa, your house is so clean,
Miss Shoop!

04:12.619 --> 04:15.420
[ Grumbling ]

04:15.455 --> 04:16.955
[ Gasps ]

04:16.990 --> 04:19.591
Miss Shoop, I didn't know you
were in the Navy.

04:19.626 --> 04:20.925
That's not me, just -- ugh!

04:20.960 --> 04:23.095
That doesn't concern you.
Just keep going!

04:30.003 --> 04:33.105
[ Gasps ]
Whoa.

04:34.774 --> 04:36.941
Clarence, what are you doing?!

04:36.976 --> 04:38.310
Ah!

04:38.345 --> 04:40.112
I'll get ya a fresh towel.

04:43.316 --> 04:45.984
Clarence, are you done?
You need to get out of my house.

04:47.153 --> 04:49.120
What? What?!

04:49.155 --> 04:50.922
[ Clanging ]

04:50.957 --> 04:52.590
[ Growls ]
- There!

04:52.625 --> 04:55.126
Now doesn't that brighten up
this boring old room?

04:55.161 --> 04:56.795
What?! G-get!
Get rid of that!

04:56.830 --> 04:58.363
I don't want anything
in this room!

04:58.398 --> 04:59.597
It's time for you to leave.

04:59.632 --> 05:01.099
You know, I bet you'd like to

05:01.134 --> 05:02.634
make some buddies, huh?

05:02.669 --> 05:04.135
I don't wanna make friends,
Clarence.

05:04.170 --> 05:06.604
But you can't just not be
friends with anybody.

05:06.639 --> 05:08.006
Ha -- you know Belson?

05:08.041 --> 05:09.974
Get out before I call
your parents.

05:10.009 --> 05:12.143
What about me?
You can be my friend!

05:12.178 --> 05:14.446
Why are you still here?!
Uh...

05:14.481 --> 05:16.848
[ Growling ]

05:16.883 --> 05:18.383
[ Screams ]
- Clarence!

05:18.418 --> 05:20.319
[ Panting ]

05:34.501 --> 05:37.469
[ Panting ]

05:37.504 --> 05:39.337
[ Clang ]
- Huh?

05:39.372 --> 05:41.940
Oh.

05:44.744 --> 05:46.344
[ Growling ]

05:46.379 --> 05:48.313
[ Sniffing ]

05:48.348 --> 05:49.681
Huh?

05:49.716 --> 05:52.350
[ Gasps ]

05:52.385 --> 05:54.853
[ Growls ]
Huh?

05:54.888 --> 05:56.554
Clarence, get away from there!

05:56.589 --> 05:58.523
[ Clarence screams ]

05:58.558 --> 06:01.159
[ Grunts ]

06:01.194 --> 06:03.795
[ Growls ]

06:07.400 --> 06:08.900
Hmm.

06:08.935 --> 06:11.603
[ Gasps ]
Wow!

06:11.638 --> 06:14.205
[ Grunting ]

06:14.240 --> 06:18.243
Oh, uh, Clarence, hon,
okay, let me do that.

06:28.121 --> 06:31.189
Mmm.

06:31.224 --> 06:33.725
Oh, my!

06:33.760 --> 06:35.760
[ Coughs ]
Mom, these beans...

06:35.795 --> 06:38.062
[ Gulps ]
Are so good.

06:38.097 --> 06:39.564
Where did you get this can?

06:39.599 --> 06:41.099
Miss Shoop made them!

06:41.134 --> 06:42.600
What?!

06:42.635 --> 06:44.536
Mmm.

06:44.571 --> 06:47.572
Wow! These are great!

06:47.607 --> 06:50.242
We gotta tell everybody about
these beans.

06:51.344 --> 06:54.746
An escaped lion is wreaking
havoc on a local neighborhood.

06:54.781 --> 06:56.915
[ Laughs ]
Dumb lion.

06:56.950 --> 06:58.883
Miss Shoop, I ate your beans!

06:58.918 --> 07:00.418
The heck!
- Clarence, get off my property.

07:00.453 --> 07:02.954
We're gonna need a lot more
for the party.

07:02.989 --> 07:05.890
Can 32B? What'd you think?
Too spicy?

07:05.925 --> 07:08.593
Nah, they were pretty much
great.

07:08.628 --> 07:10.228
Nothing beats Shoop's beans.

07:10.263 --> 07:11.930
I did add ketchup though.

07:11.965 --> 07:13.565
What, ketchup?!
Yeah, I know, right?

07:13.600 --> 07:16.501
And so, I invited all your new
friends to try your beans!

07:18.705 --> 07:20.905
This is the last straw!

07:20.940 --> 07:23.408
You have to make all of us
beans!

07:23.443 --> 07:24.476
No!

07:24.511 --> 07:25.810
Miss Shoop, wait!

07:25.845 --> 07:29.080
Your beans,
they changed my life!

07:29.115 --> 07:32.450
Think of all the other lives
they can change!

07:32.485 --> 07:33.952
[ Sighs ]

07:33.987 --> 07:37.255
The beans...
they need a home --

07:37.290 --> 07:38.957
a mouth home.

07:38.992 --> 07:41.993
No!
Lousy freeloaders!

07:42.028 --> 07:43.628
[ Growls ]

07:45.298 --> 07:46.698
Okay, hi!

07:46.733 --> 07:50.468
Um, I know everyone is really
looking forward to some beans,

07:50.503 --> 07:52.871
and I just want to say
thank you!

07:52.906 --> 07:54.939
Well, we aren't going to be
getting any.

07:54.974 --> 07:57.542
Oh, no -- all her friends!
No, wait!

07:57.577 --> 08:00.778
They're...
coming right out in, um...

08:00.813 --> 08:04.215
10 minutes, I think.

08:04.250 --> 08:07.819
I'd never give you up to those
bottom-feeding jackals.

08:07.854 --> 08:10.288
It's our time now.
Mwah!

08:10.323 --> 08:13.558
[ Intense classical
music plays ]

08:56.803 --> 08:58.202
Mmm! [ Laughs ]

08:58.237 --> 08:59.938
This is the best batch yet!

08:59.973 --> 09:01.506
Huh? Jim!

09:01.541 --> 09:02.740
[ Growls ]

09:02.775 --> 09:05.443
Huh? Huh?!

09:05.478 --> 09:07.111
All right!

09:07.146 --> 09:08.513
We got anything
to throw in here?

09:08.548 --> 09:10.682
Ready to party?!

09:10.717 --> 09:13.284
Beans, yay!

09:13.319 --> 09:15.587
Whoa!
- Who let you in here?!

09:15.622 --> 09:17.455
[ Crying ]

09:17.490 --> 09:19.557
Oh, you're gonna love
Miss Shoop.

09:19.592 --> 09:21.593
She's so cool.

09:21.628 --> 09:24.562
Clarence!

09:24.597 --> 09:29.400
All right, everyone --
get off this property!

09:29.435 --> 09:31.035
[ Growls ]

09:31.070 --> 09:33.404
Right now!

09:33.439 --> 09:35.873
[ Screaming ]

09:35.908 --> 09:38.076
[ Engines starting ]

09:38.111 --> 09:39.744
[ Screaming continues ]

09:39.779 --> 09:41.112
Clarence!

09:41.147 --> 09:43.748
You're banned from my house
and this block!

09:43.783 --> 09:45.583
But Jeff lives on this block!

09:45.618 --> 09:47.418
Your friendship with Jeff
is over!

09:47.453 --> 09:48.720
All right.

09:48.755 --> 09:51.255
I'm sorry about your house.

09:51.290 --> 09:53.891
I just wanted to help you
make some friends.

09:53.926 --> 09:56.761
[ Sighs ]

09:56.796 --> 09:58.763
You see this bean, Clarence?

09:58.798 --> 10:00.431
Yes.

10:00.466 --> 10:02.767
Well, I grew this bean myself.

10:02.802 --> 10:05.937
It was created by the greatest
bean-maker ever known --

10:05.972 --> 10:07.672
me.

10:07.707 --> 10:09.240
I love me.

10:09.275 --> 10:11.743
People mess up the beans,
Clarence.

10:11.778 --> 10:14.278
All I need is beans -- and me.

10:14.313 --> 10:16.781
Wow.
That's kind of --

10:16.816 --> 10:19.851
Now go away! And take this
tarnished bean with you!

10:19.886 --> 10:21.586
[ Grunts ]

10:21.621 --> 10:23.921
Reporter:
Live from downtown Aberdale,

10:23.956 --> 10:25.590
where a bean-frenzied mob

10:25.625 --> 10:28.026
is lying waste to
a local food court.

10:28.061 --> 10:30.295
[ Laughs ]

10:43.476 --> 10:46.944
Oh. Uh, I don't think Miss Shoop
wants any visitors.

10:46.979 --> 10:48.546
So you can just go away.

10:48.581 --> 10:50.848
No, wait, she's --
she's my niece!

10:50.883 --> 10:52.283
I don't think so.

10:52.318 --> 10:53.818
You don't understand.
Go away, go away.

10:53.853 --> 10:56.054
No visitors allowed.

10:56.089 --> 10:58.323
Get out of here.

11:00.226 --> 11:02.594
[ Shoop laughing ]

11:04.297 --> 11:06.831
♪ Early to bed ♪

11:06.866 --> 11:06.898
♪ Early to rise ♪

11:08.067 --> 11:11.836
♪ Early to rise ♪

11:11.871 --> 11:15.006
♪ Picking my nose ♪
